name: Five Year Cycle
description: Meme coin launched on BSC chain. Coin narrative is to attract crypto degens who think that we are in 5 year crypto cycle. Why? We believe that 4 year cycle is no longer valid, and that we are now in 5 Year Cycle. $FYC team is going to strive to create cult and movement regarding that whole narrative and have fun with community content while doing so. Project has it's mascot called Luna, who is anime themed waifu. She is face of the meme coin and present in all funny content.
